	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_session_count_pause">
		<text>Session: count pauses</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_session_count_pause_desc">
		<text>Include time spent in the pause menu, MCM, console, or alt-tabbed in the session timer (measured by wall clock). Total Time Played never counts it.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_session_count_loadings">
		<text>Session: count loading screens</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_session_count_loadings_desc">
		<text>Include loading screens, level transitions, main-menu time between loads, and short game restarts in the session timer. Total Time Played never counts it.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_session_break_min">
		<text>Session: break threshold (minutes)</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_session_break_min_desc">
		<text>The session timer keeps running through loads, level transitions, and even game restarts. It starts over only after you have been away longer than this (game closed, crash, or idling in the main menu that long).</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_units">
		<text>Time detail</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_units_desc">
		<text>How detailed the time values are. Applies immediately.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_lst_itts_units_hm">
		<text>Hours, minutes</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_lst_itts_units_h">
