	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_b">
		<text>Custom color: blue</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_b_desc">
		<text>Blue component of the custom clock color (0-255).</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_enabled">
		<text>PDA notifications</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_enabled_desc">
		<text>Send a PDA message from It's Time To Stop when the session crosses the thresholds below: the time left at the good threshold, and a reminder to stop at the bad one. One message per crossing.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_good">
		<text>"Good" threshold (minutes)</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_good_desc">
		<text>Crossing this session length sends a PDA warning with the time left until the bad threshold. The progressive clock color also switches to its middle stage here.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_bad">
		<text>"Bad" threshold (minutes)</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_bad_desc">
		<text>Crossing this session length sends the "session exceeded" PDA message. The progressive clock color also switches to its final stage here.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_repeat">
		<text>Repeated session end notification</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_repeat_desc">
		<text>Keep re-sending the "session exceeded" message after the bad threshold, at the interval below.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_repeat_min">
		<text>Repeat interval (minutes)</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_repeat_min_desc">
		<text>How much more play time passes between repeated "session exceeded" messages.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_sound">
		<text>Notification sound</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_notify_sound_desc">
		<text>Play the PDA beep with the notification.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive">
		<text>Progressive color by session length</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_desc">
		<text>Change the clock color automatically as your current session crosses the notification thresholds above. Overrides the color preset and custom color.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_clr_good">
		<text>Stage color: below good threshold</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_clr_good_desc">
		<text>Clock color while the session is shorter than the good threshold.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_clr_mid">
		<text>Stage color: between thresholds</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_clr_mid_desc">
		<text>Clock color between the good and bad thresholds.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_clr_bad">
		<text>Stage color: past bad threshold</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_itts_stat_clock_progressive_clr_bad_desc">
		<text>Clock color once the session passes the bad threshold.</text>
	</string>
